{"_id":"I5icA9Bh1NImlhwj","name":"Storm Greatsword +1","permission":{"default":0,"K5dQgTzG7G3s9UY1":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>Forged by the expert hand of Blackreach's dwarf smith, this weapon is made of the hide and bones of a young dragon that fell in battle to a Paladin's might. Imbued with its Draconis Fundamentum, the greatsword absorbs ambient energy that the wielder can deliver in thunderous blows.</em></p>\n<p>You have a bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[homebrew.hbitems.68ue99FS14ByTN18]{Storm Strike.}</strong> In addition, this weapon has 3 charges recovered on a long rest. When you hit an attack, you can choose to spend one charge to deal an additional 1d8 lightning damage, or spend the 3 charges and deal an additional 3d8 lightning damage on a single hit. If the weapon is used in this way, it can't regain charges until 7 days have passed.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"KalinorIV","quantity":1,"weight":6,"price":1000,"attuned":false,"equipped":true,"rarity":"Rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":1,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6r<3 + @mod +1","slashing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","properties":{"hvy":true,"two":true,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"ver":false},"proficient":true,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"flags":{"gwmMacro":null},"img":"modules/homebrew/icons/items/greatsword-crossguard-blue-